divs: Sighting DetailsI have taken pictures every night at the same time for a couple of nights now. When I take the pictures there are some times alot of them and sometimes less. I have pictures of ufos where you can see there faces and bodies of the aliens and I have 1 where the ufo looks like human heads. These things that I have taken pictures can not be seen by human, only when I look at the pictures do they show up. Dates beginning 3-8-09 and I have and will continue to take the photos each night. I am at a loss of words, the photos have been shown to my kids and my wife refuses to look at them because they freak her out.
